{"tid":1281871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位想自殺嘅巴絲","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T19:24:27.000Z","uid":112078,"like":115,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"762d52380e3a75d687978cb44bc173a69b70f615","tid":1281871,"uid":112078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"自殺，冇錯，係需要好大嘅勇氣<br />\n<br />\n要製造社會迴響，都不失為一個方法<br />\n<br />\n但想離開人世前,可唔可以先了解一下我地對家嘅態度<br />\n<br />\n第一個跳樓-林鄭冇反應<br />\n第二個跳樓-佢冇反應<br />\n第三個跳樓-一樣冇反應<br />\n<br />\n如果你同我地講話為咗表達訴求而要跳樓嘅,我請你地先諗清楚個權衡輕重<br />\n<br />\n捨身達義定係執返條命日日同政府死過好啲？<br />\n<br />\n係呢1分鐘我可以好肯定咁同你講：你哋就算跳晒落去，佢都一樣唔會比到回應<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">值嗎？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所謂革命唔係一日就可以完成，回顧番一下歷史<br />\n美國獨立搞咗幾多年？國民黨搞咗幾多次先可以推翻清政府？再睇下我哋嘅共同敵人共產黨，佢花咗幾多時間先至可以從國民黨手下死過翻生，最後仲可以推翻國民政府，成為中華地區執政黨。<br />\n<br />\n呢一場仗，我哋要留嘅唔係單單一個口號，一個精神<br />\n係每一個人堅定不移嘅決心，每一個人對未來嘅憧憬同盼望，更重要嘅係每一位人既赤子之心同生命呀！<br />\n<br />\n要同人打仗首先你一定要比人哋活得更長命<br />\n<br />\n希望你哋永遠都要記得，我地香港人既路<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊行 一齊走 我地一個都不能小</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好諗錯嘢啦，返黎啦！我地個個都等緊你一同抗爭 一同見證成功"},{"pid":"f9b6727dbf86492e3637fa78f13a4b8315924f1f","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"025637169c32497b797b874b02136c179e72d48b","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c312c9dab0684d4443d064d3338c225e206db988","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff5742a068c8f79197b168b76176a11a06b402de","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8723bec52445bcf909d94bda23d91b9faa2ed94","tid":1281871,"uid":112078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e41c276f3f670478d5152d007c138a68b357848a","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a716de966c01fd653fab0ed73a61400de3468764","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"157db477b0a04106032abdebdb87314f020f7c59","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc7e24f5508594bbb8d7fa98364c68762dbb994a","tid":1281871,"uid":225144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲真係唔好諗咁多呀，我同大家一樣都好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果你地真係好頂唔順既，不如入來呢個tg gp，我地一齊面對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=b292a728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg</a>"},{"pid":"2ae276a3003f1e3a5e3f005d63218e83ecbb3c28","tid":1281871,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79bc0192793d08e6aa85f20248e39a42ac8a2dc9","tid":1281871,"uid":161685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b00c0cd9792a029fb5fa7e02de464e09ce59ce1d","tid":128